trans-unit.source: Disable RTE: If this option is set the config for RTE will not load automatically. Include "FILE:EXT:bootstrap_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/RTE.tsconfig" in your PageTsConfig to load the config manually.

Disable TCEFORM: If this option is set the config for TCEFORM will not load automatically. Include "FILE:EXT:bootstrap_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/TCEFORM.tsconfig" in your PageTsConfig to load the config manually.

Disable TCEMAIN: If this option is set the config for TCEMAIN will not load automatically. Include "FILE:EXT:bootstrap_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/TCEMAIN.tsconfig" in your PageTsConfig to load the config manually.

Disable BackendLayouts: If this option is set the included backend layouts will not load automatically. Include "FILE:EXT:bootstrap_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/Mod/WebLayout/BackendLayouts.tsconfig" in your PageTsConfig to load the config manually.

Disable Content Element PageTS Configuration: If this option is set, the included configuration for content elements will not be loaded automatically. Include "FILE:EXT:bootstrap_package/Configuration/TsConfig/Page/ContentElement/All.tsconfig" in your PageTsConfig to load the config manually.

Disable Processing of LESS/Scss files: WARNING: If this option is set there no more automatic processing of LESS/Scss files in the frontend. You will need to provide CSS files instead or handle the processing of the LESS/Scss files yourself.
Disable local Google-Font cache: If this option is set, Google Fonts will not be cached on the server.
Disable WebFontLoader: If this option is set, there will be no additional processing of WebFonts.
